&lt;/svg&gt;∈S,&lt;svg xmlns:xlink=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink&#34; width=&#34;3.656ex&#34; height=&#34;3.843ex&#34; style=&#34;vertical-align: -0.671ex;&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 -1365.4 1574.2 1654.5&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; focusable=&#34;false&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;MathJax-SVG-1-Title&#34;&gt;
